formula:
\begin{array}{lcr}
BaseDamageModifier = floor(BaseMaxDamage + ChaosGauntlets + Charge)\\
PrimaryMagicDamage = floor(BaseDamageModifier * (1 + minimum(1,(VisibleBonuses - Void) * ShadowBonus) + Void + Salve + Avarice + SmokeBattlestaff + VirtusRobesAncientBonus))\\
SecondaryMagicDamage = floor(PrimaryMagicDamage * (1 + AhrimsDamned + Slayer + SceptreWilderness))\\
TertiaryMagicDamage = floor(SecondaryMagicDamage * (1 + AccursedSceptreSpecialAttack))\\
HitRoll = floor(random(0,TertiaryMagicDamage))\\
PostHitRoll = floor(HitRoll * (1 + TomeOfFire + TomeOfWater + MarkOfDarkness))\\
AppliedHit = floor(PostHitRoll * (1 + CastleWarsBraclet))\\
\end{array}

\begin{array}{lcr}

SecondaryMagicDamage = floor(PrimaryMagicDamage * (1 + AhrimsDamned + Slayer + SceptreWilderness))\\
TertiaryMagicDamage = floor(SecondaryMagicDamage * (1 + AccursedSceptreSpecialAttack))\\

\end{array}

formula:
\begin{align}
Base &= \frac{1}{4} \times (Defence + Hitpoints + \lfloor \frac{1}{2} \times Prayer \rfloor) \\
Melee &= \frac{13}{40} \times (Attack + Strength) \\
Range &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Ranged \rfloor \\
Mage &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Magic \rfloor \\
Final &= \lfloor Base + max(Melee, Range, Mage) \rfloor
\end{align}
raw:
\begin{align}
Base &= \frac{1}{4} \times (Defence + Hitpoints + \lfloor \frac{1}{2} \times Prayer \rfloor) \\
Melee &= \frac{13}{40} \times (Attack + Strength) \\
Range &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Ranged \rfloor \\
Mage &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Magic \rfloor \\
Final &= \lfloor Base + max(Melee, Range, Mage) \rfloor
\end{align}
